title: Royal Time
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian restaurant with a large vegetarian menu section where some of these dises can be prepared vegan such as the aloo baigan, simla aloo, baigan achari, pumpkin masala, veg jalfrezi, and veg vindaloo. Vegetable oil is used in the preparation of all meals. The roti and saffron rice is suitable for vegans. Avoid the fried entrees as the oil is shared with non-veg items.
